c: 18
v: 21
t: "Uku niko twaba menyesheje kubantu kugira ngo bamenye yuko indagano y’Imana ari iy’ukuri kandi umusi w’imperuka atankeka urimwo, mugihe bashamirana hagati yabo kubera ijambo ryabo, abandi baca bavuga bati:- nimwubake inyubakwa hejuru yabo, kuko Umuremyi wabo arabazi neza, nabo baca bavuga bamwe batsinda k’urubanza rwabo bati:- ntankeka twebwe tuzokwubaka isengero hejuru yabo"